{"word":"ἀπανίστημι","slug":"ἀπανίστημι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπανίστημι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to make rise up and depart, send away</i>, <el>τὴν στρατιήν</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with aor2 and <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>, and <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a>, <i>to arise and go away, depart, leave one's country, emigrate</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}